data.value:
This is Frost and his adorable factor is through the roof !! He is a less than a year old, Lionhead mix who came to the Rescue from the local Animal Shelter.
Frost is a snuggle bug who is already neutered and little box trained.
His fur is soft as can be and will need some rushing from his 'fur-ever' family to keep him as handsome as he is now.
